- The second interim analysis (IA2) is the FA for PFS and will be performed after approximately 468 PFS events have been observed, approximately 26 months after first patient enrolled. An interim analysis of OS will be performed; it is estimated that approximately 332 deaths will be observed.
- The FA will evaluate OS only and will be performed after approximately 416 deaths have been observed. It is estimated that this will occur approximately 35 months after enrollment begins.
